videos.description: Georgia's Amanze Ngumezi blocks Obi Toppin on one end of the court and then runs to the other end to score a putback shot, drawing a foul in the process.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Ngumezi takes over on both ends of the court) 2019/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ngumezi takes over on both ends of the court.

videos.description: Dayton's Obi Toppin gets nothing the bottom of the net as he drains a 3-pointer just before the shot clock expires.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Toppin knocks down the corner 3) 2019/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toppin knocks down the corner 3
